##DISPLAYNAME Provision All XVMs
##DESCRIPTION Wipes current installations and provisions clean images for all XVMs.

provision the cardservice-1a xvm
configure the cardservice-1a xvm
deploy to the cardservice-1a xvm

provision the cardservice-1b xvm
configure the cardservice-1b xvm
deploy to the cardservice-1b xvm

provision the customerservice-1a xvm
configure the customerservice-1a xvm
deploy to the customerservice-1a xvm

provision the customerservice-1b xvm
configure the customerservice-1b xvm
deploy to the customerservice-1b xvm

provision the customerseeder xvm
configure the customerseeder xvm
deploy to the customerseeder xvm

provision the driver xvm
configure the driver xvm
deploy to the driver xvm

